00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,360
to want to be a mother.

283
00:15:50,159 --> 00:15:51,240
Dear.

284
00:15:52,399 --> 00:15:54,000
I really want to be a mother.

285
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:09,200
Shall we go see the doctor...

286
00:16:09,679 --> 00:16:10,960
for a checkup next week?

287
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:14,399
Okay.

288
00:16:15,799 --> 00:16:16,840
I'll listen to you.

289
00:16:22,279 --> 00:16:24,559
(Energy City)

290
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:29,360
Energy City is so beautiful.

291
00:16:30,759 --> 00:16:33,759
Those who live there have their own drivers.

292
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:36,919
They look gorgeous every day...

293
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:40,319
as they frequent various high-end hotels and restaurants.

294
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:41,918
(Agency information)

295
00:16:41,919 --> 00:16:43,879
Their biggest problem...

296
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:47,679
