297
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:50,000
I'm so envious.

298
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:53,440
Do you like Energy City?

299
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,278
I do.

300
00:16:56,279 --> 00:16:57,360
I love it.

301
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:59,280
Do you want to rent or buy it?

302
00:17:01,159 --> 00:17:02,240
Rent it.

303
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:05,839
Aside from renting and buying,

304
00:17:05,890 --> 00:17:07,450
we also offer other sales methods here.

305
00:17:07,559 --> 00:17:08,559
Do you want to try it?

306
00:17:11,279 --> 00:17:12,359
Sure.

307
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:15,680
First, throw away your books.

308
00:17:16,319 --> 00:17:17,410
Any girl with a mind...

309
00:17:17,559 --> 00:17:18,599
and ideals...

310
00:17:18,839 --> 00:17:20,119
can't live in Energy City.

311
00:17:23,359 --> 00:17:24,359
That's easy.

312
00:17:25,039 --> 00:17:27,119
Second, you need to learn to disguise your feelings.

313
00:17:27,519 --> 00:17:30,079
You can't let joy or anger be visible on your face.

314
00:17:40,170 --> 00:17:41,170
How about this?

315
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:42,720
That's not enough.

316
00:17:43,170 --> 00:17:44,200
Not enough?

317
00:17:44,279 --> 00:17:45,839
Wearing a mask is really uncomfortable.

318
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,519
Focus on the key point.

319
00:17:49,170 --> 00:17:50,200
You're not smiling.

320
00:17:50,839 --> 00:17:52,519
You have to smile all the time.

321
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:56,039
You have to know how to make someone happy.

322
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:08,000
How about this?

323
00:18:11,960 --> 00:18:19,279
(Energy City)

324
00:18:19,319 --> 00:18:21,000
You have to sit still.

325
00:18:21,079 --> 00:18:22,119
Don't move.

326
00:18:23,650 --> 00:18:25,890
You have to turn a blind eye.

327
00:18:27,650 --> 00:18:29,720
You have to stop thinking.

328
00:18:37,799 --> 00:18:39,200
Congratulations, Sun Xiao Han.

329
00:18:39,519 --> 00:18:41,410
You've successfully checked into Energy City.

330
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:44,200
Enjoy your stay.

331
00:19:04,079 --> 00:19:08,079
(Anji Beef Restaurant)

332
00:19:08,170 --> 00:19:09,409
This place is newly opened.

333
00:19:09,410 --> 00:19:10,480
We haven't tried it yet.

334
00:19:10,799 --> 00:19:11,839
He made the choice,

335
00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:14,095
so if the food is bad, we can hold him accountable.

336
00:19:14,119 --> 00:19:15,890
I recently read a new study.

337
00:19:16,119 --> 00:19:19,240
It claims that attractive people are also good eaters.

338
00:19:19,599 --> 00:19:21,519
I have faith in your boyfriend.

339
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:23,200
Here.

340
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:25,000
Why are you smiling?

341
00:19:25,001 --> 00:19:26,039
She's praising you.

342
00:19:26,279 --> 00:19:27,359
Say thank you.

343
00:19:27,890 --> 00:19:28,890
Thank you, Han Han.

344
00:19:29,519 --> 00:19:32,170
Nan Nan told me that you're her best friend,

345
00:19:32,410 --> 00:19:33,850
so I picked this hot pot restaurant.

346
00:19:33,890 --> 00:19:34,959
We can chat while eating.

347
00:19:34,960 --> 00:19:35,960
Okay.

348
00:19:36,839 --> 00:19:38,480
I'll make the condiments for you.

349
00:19:44,410 --> 00:19:45,439
What do you think?

350
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:46,480
Tell me honestly.

351
00:19:48,240 --> 00:19:49,559
Not bad.

352
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:52,519
I'll go too.

353
00:20:04,410 --> 00:20:06,039
By the way, can I ask you out alone?

354
00:20:09,079 --> 00:20:10,079
It's for Nan Nan.

355
00:20:10,839 --> 00:20:11,890
I want to know...

356
00:20:12,079 --> 00:20:13,079
about the guy...

357
00:20:13,079 --> 00:20:14,079
she was with for seven years.

358
00:20:14,080 --> 00:20:15,170
What is he like?

359
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:18,079
I don't know him well.

360
00:20:18,410 --> 00:20:19,575
We only had dinner a few times.

361
00:20:19,599 --> 00:20:20,775
He didn't even add me on WeChat.

362
00:20:20,799 --> 00:20:22,440
We're just friends on Weibo.

363
00:20:22,480 --> 00:20:23,600
I don't know much about him.

364
00:20:25,119 --> 00:20:26,720
Can you tell me his Weibo?

365
00:20:29,440 --> 00:20:30,599
Why do you need his Weibo?

366
00:20:30,759 --> 00:20:31,839
To love her.

367
00:20:32,170 --> 00:20:33,480
Nowadays,

368
00:20:33,650 --> 00:20:35,610
there aren't as many pure-hearted lovers anymore.

369
00:20:36,650 --> 00:20:39,240
You're doing this for your greed and caution.

370
00:20:39,839 --> 00:20:41,480
Love is also a kind of greed.

371
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:42,799
Right?

372
00:20:46,599 --> 00:20:47,680
I'll go ahead.

373
00:20:58,559 --> 00:21:00,200
Why are you taking so long?

374
00:21:00,410 --> 00:21:02,559
It's nothing. We were just chatting.

375
00:21:08,519 --> 00:21:09,599
This won't do.

376
00:21:10,079 --> 00:21:11,119
I'm so full.

377
00:21:12,599 --> 00:21:13,959
I've decided that starting tomorrow,

378
00:21:13,960 --> 00:21:15,000
I won't have dinner.

379
00:21:15,200 --> 00:21:16,240
The Internet says...

380
00:21:16,650 --> 00:21:17,976
that having a cheat meal occasionally...

381
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,000
can help with weight loss.

382
00:21:19,001 --> 00:21:20,240
(Nothing I Can Do About You)

383
00:21:20,319 --> 00:21:22,279
Every meal you have is a cheat meal.

384
00:21:22,519 --> 00:21:23,519
If you never feel full,

385
00:21:23,520 --> 00:21:25,055
how can you have the energy to lose weight?

386
00:21:25,079 --> 00:21:26,480
Nothing I Can Do About You.

387
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:27,799
Is it your Weibo?

388
00:21:28,650 --> 00:21:29,650
How did you find it?

389
00:21:29,720 --> 00:21:31,039
We just played a small game.

390
00:21:31,410 --> 00:21:33,799
She told me her Weibo and asked if I could find yours.

391
00:21:35,170 --> 00:21:36,200
He's just bored.

392
00:21:37,240 --> 00:21:38,240
Are you still on Weibo?

393
00:21:38,279 --> 00:21:39,439
I haven't used it in a while.

394
00:21:40,410 --> 00:21:41,480
It's just for fun.

395
00:21:44,319 --> 00:21:45,319
Here.

396
00:21:48,200 --> 00:21:50,039
You should eat too. Have one.

397
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:51,480
Beef ball.

398
00:21:51,481 --> 00:21:52,519
Thank you.

399
00:21:56,799 --> 00:21:58,200
(Nothing I Can Do About You)

400
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:11,679
(What do you think of him?)

401
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:17,278
(Nan Nan: What do you think of him?)

402
00:22:17,279 --> 00:22:25,200
(He treats you well, seems smart, and looks good too.)

403
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:45,159
(There's something I need to tell you.)

404
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:49,518
(He asked me about Gao Peng privately, )

405
00:22:49,519 --> 00:22:51,359
(but I didn't say anything.)

406
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:26,959
By the way,

407
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:29,480
