408
00:23:29,720 --> 00:23:30,720
Sure.

409
00:23:31,119 --> 00:23:32,136
Do you want to join us, Han Han?

410
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:34,479
I don't want to be a third wheel.

411
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:36,000
- I'm not going. - Are you sure?

412
00:23:37,519 --> 00:23:38,519
It's just the two of us then.

413
00:23:38,519 --> 00:23:39,519
Okay.

414
00:23:56,279 --> 00:23:57,400
