417
00:24:02,079 --> 00:24:03,159
I want to eat rice noodles.

418
00:24:03,319 --> 00:24:04,400
Rice noodles.

419
00:24:05,599 --> 00:24:06,799
It's so beautiful here.

420
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:08,319
Here, let me take a photo of you.

421
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:22,039
It's nice.

422
00:24:36,519 --> 00:24:38,359
They think I'm too fat.

423
00:24:38,799 --> 00:24:40,279
You're fat?

424
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:42,400
This one.

425
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:43,799
Look at the nostrils.

426
00:24:44,240 --> 00:24:45,240
It's obviously you.

427
00:24:48,440 --> 00:24:49,640
Which one do you like?

428
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:52,200
They're all good.

429
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:55,079
You have to pick one.

430
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:02,200
This one then.

431
00:25:02,720 --> 00:25:03,799
We both look good.

432
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:11,720
All right.

433
00:25:12,119 --> 00:25:14,160
Now, whenever my phone gets a notification,

434
00:25:14,279 --> 00:25:16,440
