435
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:20,720
Should I also do the same?

436
00:25:21,240 --> 00:25:23,119
Well. It's up to you.

437
00:25:34,319 --> 00:25:35,960
Is this your new Weibo account?

438
00:25:37,119 --> 00:25:38,838
I thought only college students use this.

439
00:25:38,839 --> 00:25:39,920
(Yi Loves Zhi Nan)

440
00:25:41,480 --> 00:25:42,920
Just think of it as a diary.

441
00:25:43,359 --> 00:25:45,079
If you run away one day,

442
00:25:46,839 --> 00:25:49,000
there's still something to reminisce about.

443
00:25:50,039 --> 00:25:51,159
Sorry to keep you waiting.

444
00:25:51,160 --> 00:25:52,160
It's okay.

445
00:25:55,680 --> 00:25:56,720
Thank you.

446
00:25:59,119 --> 00:26:00,119
It smells so good.

447
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:01,400
Thank you.

448
00:26:01,401 --> 00:26:02,480
It's okay.

449
00:26:09,200 --> 00:26:11,159
(Su Su: I'll come back tomorrow.)

450
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:17,839
(Okay. I'll go pick you up.)

451
00:26:21,039 --> 00:26:23,079
By the way, I have to work overtime tomorrow night.

452
00:26:23,519 --> 00:26:24,559
It's okay.

453
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:26,199
It just so happens that one of my colleagues...

454
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:27,200
