455
00:26:27,201 --> 00:26:29,079
She invited me to her house.

456
00:26:30,359 --> 00:26:31,598
I'll pick you up after dinner.

457
00:26:31,599 --> 00:26:32,680
Sure.

458
00:26:34,079 --> 00:26:38,079
(Huanking Business Building)

459
00:26:54,119 --> 00:26:59,519
The groom from the Ming Dynasty is looking at the bride

460
00:26:59,960 --> 00:27:06,759
