461
00:27:07,319 --> 00:27:10,759
It's the end of the world

462
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:15,119
May the lovers will forever be together

463
00:27:15,160 --> 00:27:17,960
I'll bow to my husband

464
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:20,839
Cross our arms and raise our cups

465
00:27:28,920 --> 00:27:29,960
Working overtime again?

466
00:27:31,640 --> 00:27:34,359
How much money do you actually want to make?

467
00:27:34,519 --> 00:27:35,719
Don't you need to rest at all?

468
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,078
That's amazing.

469
00:27:38,079 --> 00:27:39,160
Stop teasing me.

470
00:27:39,759 --> 00:27:42,400
Ren Jianhui and Bai Xuexian can sing better than me.

471
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:44,079
Ren Jianhui.

472
00:27:44,920 --> 00:27:47,079
Do you know him?

473
00:27:47,160 --> 00:27:48,239
Of course.

474
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,456
He's the first Cantonese opera singer.

475
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:50,480
- Yes. - Before I came to Hong Kong,

476
00:27:50,481 --> 00:27:51,519
I did some research.

477
00:27:51,799 --> 00:27:53,759
I've even heard them sing "Princess Cheung Ping".

478
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:55,176
Although I didn't understand all of it,

479
00:27:55,200 --> 00:27:56,598
