480
00:27:56,599 --> 00:27:57,880
You have a good taste.

481
00:27:58,440 --> 00:28:00,279
I made some milk tea. Do you want to try it?

482
00:28:00,319 --> 00:28:01,440
- Sure. - Come on.

483
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:08,319
It shows how much you love your daughter

484
00:28:09,200 --> 00:28:12,759
The prince consort kept refusing to express his feelings

485
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:17,960
It shows how much he loves his wife...

486
00:28:18,039 --> 00:28:19,119
Mr. Zhong.

487
00:28:19,279 --> 00:28:20,519
How many children do you have?

488
00:28:22,359 --> 00:28:23,359
Three daughters.

489
00:28:25,279 --> 00:28:27,359
They have been married to places all over the world.

490
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:30,119
None of them stayed in Hong Kong.

491
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:32,720
Here.

492
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,680
Let me pour you some milk.

493
00:28:37,559 --> 00:28:39,599
This is the legendary Hong Kong-style milk tea.

494
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:40,799
Here.

495
00:28:41,200 --> 00:28:43,559
This is called Mr. Zhong's milk tea.

496
00:28:45,160 --> 00:28:46,559
After you try it,

497
00:28:47,359 --> 00:28:49,880
you won't drink any other milk tea.

498
00:28:56,359 --> 00:28:57,359
It's good.

499
00:28:59,400 --> 00:29:01,039
My daughters like it too.

500
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:04,960
They must be very happy to be your daughters.

501
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:08,240
As long as they're happy.

502
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:19,200
Are you not happy?

503
00:29:23,400 --> 00:29:26,319
Had a fight with your boyfriend?

504
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:30,519
We broke up.

505
00:29:33,039 --> 00:29:34,240
It's fated...

506
00:29:34,519 --> 00:29:36,160
