507
00:29:38,039 --> 00:29:39,440
I'm the one without luck.

508
00:29:41,759 --> 00:29:43,160
He's actually a nice guy.

509
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:45,960
Maybe...

510
00:29:46,559 --> 00:29:48,119
I'm not content.

511
00:29:48,839 --> 00:29:50,440
I left him behind...

512
00:29:51,039 --> 00:29:52,160
and came to Hong Kong alone.

513
00:29:54,279 --> 00:29:56,920
So you didn't like him for a long time.

514
00:29:59,559 --> 00:30:01,199
He didn't like me for a long time either.

515
00:30:02,440 --> 00:30:03,440
He probably...

516
00:30:06,839 --> 00:30:09,119
