517
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:21,240
Do you want a pineapple bun?

518
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:22,640
Sure.

519
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:24,759
You'll have to wait.

520
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:27,680
The pineapple bun needs to be warmed up to taste good.

521
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:34,240
Actually,

522
00:30:35,559 --> 00:30:36,640
in life,

523
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:40,200
we should cry hard...

524
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:42,119
and laugh hard.

525
00:30:43,319 --> 00:30:44,440
After crying and laughing,

526
00:30:44,920 --> 00:30:46,000
everything will be fine.

527
00:30:56,799 --> 00:30:57,799
Mr. Zhong.

528
00:30:58,480 --> 00:31:01,039
I'm going back to Jiangzhou tomorrow to see him one last time.

529
00:31:02,200 --> 00:31:03,279
What's wrong?

530
00:31:03,799 --> 00:31:05,160
Is he very sick?

531
00:31:06,599 --> 00:31:08,078
I'm going back to pack my things.

532
00:31:08,079 --> 00:31:09,439
Then I'm coming back to Hong Kong.

533
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:11,160
You scared me.

534
00:31:13,759 --> 00:31:15,079
When I come back this time,

535
00:31:15,119 --> 00:31:16,318
I'll bring you good food.

536
00:31:16,319 --> 00:31:17,359
Sure.

537
00:31:17,960 --> 00:31:19,880
I can't bring crayfish.

538
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:22,000
Don't bring them even if you can.

539
00:31:22,160 --> 00:31:23,599
I prefer big lobsters.

540
00:31:33,279 --> 00:31:34,319
Here you go.

541
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:37,480
I'll put some butter...

542
00:31:38,240 --> 00:31:39,599
for you.

543
00:31:39,759 --> 00:31:40,999
That's what makes it delicious.

544
00:31:44,359 --> 00:31:45,400
It smells so good.

545
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:47,240
Okay.

546
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:51,999
Eating this late at night is fattening.

547
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:53,038
No, it won't.

548
00:31:53,039 --> 00:31:54,720
This butter is famous.

549
00:31:55,079 --> 00:31:56,079
Free-fat butter.

550
00:31:57,559 --> 00:31:59,160
Here, try it.

551
00:32:00,599 --> 00:32:01,640
Here.

552
00:32:04,799 --> 00:32:07,359
Mr. Zhong's pineapple bun is the best in Hong Kong.

553
00:32:07,480 --> 00:32:08,559
Well said.

554
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:10,079
The best in Hong Kong.

555
00:32:41,559 --> 00:32:42,839
How's the food there?

556
00:32:45,519 --> 00:32:46,519
It's quite good.

557
00:32:49,559 --> 00:32:51,000
The food is good.

558
00:32:51,759 --> 00:32:52,839
It's not expensive either.

559
00:32:53,400 --> 00:32:54,720
Stop eating out.

560
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:57,839
Learn how to cook.

561
00:32:58,240 --> 00:32:59,319
I'm learning.

562
00:33:08,079 --> 00:33:09,359
I learned two new dishes.

563
00:33:09,519 --> 00:33:10,839
I'll make them for you tonight.

