00:33:11,920 --> 00:33:12,920
No.

565
00:33:13,279 --> 00:33:14,839
Let me cook tonight.

566
00:33:15,559 --> 00:33:17,759
The dishes and everything are all ready.

567
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:43,759
Thank you.

568
00:34:09,329 --> 00:34:10,440
The soup is fresh.

569
00:34:12,840 --> 00:34:15,440
I bought beef bones and boiled them all afternoon.

570
00:34:16,199 --> 00:34:17,199
Thank you.

571
00:34:21,840 --> 00:34:23,655
Thinking that you're leaving just like that...

572
00:34:23,679 --> 00:34:24,769
makes me sad.

573
00:34:31,880 --> 00:34:32,880
Is that girl...

574
00:34:35,119 --> 00:34:36,199
your new girlfriend?

575
00:34:39,289 --> 00:34:40,519
She's quite cute.

576
00:34:46,159 --> 00:34:47,440
Actually, I already knew.

577
00:34:51,289 --> 00:34:53,769
The night before I called you to break up,

578
00:34:54,880 --> 00:34:57,769
I called to ask you for the Youku verification code.

579
00:34:58,559 --> 00:34:59,639
She answered the call.

580
00:35:01,440 --> 00:35:03,480
But she didn't sound very nice.

581
00:35:04,840 --> 00:35:05,879
What did she say?

582
00:35:05,880 --> 00:35:06,880
Nothing.

583
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:09,039
I don't care anymore.

584
00:35:14,519 --> 00:35:17,519
(He Zhi Nan)

585
00:35:24,519 --> 00:35:26,199
Yi Peng, are you coming to pick me up?

586
00:35:26,769 --> 00:35:27,769
I'm in a meeting.

587
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:37,079
He Zhi Nan.

588
00:35:39,079 --> 00:35:40,079
Is that her name?

589
00:35:49,519 --> 00:35:51,159
To be honest, the first time...

590
00:35:52,119 --> 00:35:55,239
I heard another woman's voice on your phone,

591
00:35:56,639 --> 00:35:59,239
the anger and sadness I felt...

592
00:36:00,329 --> 00:36:01,400
were much stronger...

593
00:36:02,809 --> 00:36:04,199
than I expected.

594
00:36:06,199 --> 00:36:07,400
I felt...

595
00:36:08,289 --> 00:36:10,920
so humiliated.

596
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:14,680
I initially wanted to call and confront you,

597
00:36:15,769 --> 00:36:17,679
but then I thought there was nothing to say.

598
00:36:19,329 --> 00:36:20,856
That's why you broke up with me the next day.

599
00:36:20,880 --> 00:36:22,719
Didn't you prepare for this?

600
00:36:26,920 --> 00:36:27,960
Han Su.

601
00:36:28,880 --> 00:36:30,239
You know I love you, right?

602
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:32,400
But I'm aware that...

603
00:36:32,809 --> 00:36:34,480
I can't provide what you want.

604
00:36:34,769 --> 00:36:35,969
Perhaps it's better to let go.

605
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:37,039
Let go?

606
00:36:37,360 --> 00:36:39,360
Aren't you already looking for someone new?

607
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:41,520
What about your relocation to Hong Kong?

608
00:36:43,199 --> 00:36:45,319
It wasn't the firm that transferred you there, right?

609
00:36:45,880 --> 00:36:47,400
You applied on your own...

610
00:36:47,769 --> 00:36:49,920
and secured it through fierce competition, right?

611
00:36:53,239 --> 00:36:54,239
So...

612
00:36:55,519 --> 00:36:56,840
when it comes to planning ahead,

613
00:36:57,199 --> 00:36:58,289
we're pretty much even.

614
00:37:06,599 --> 00:37:08,400
That girl comes from a rich family, right?

615
00:37:09,679 --> 00:37:11,519
She's a low-profile rich heiress.

616
00:37:12,519 --> 00:37:14,719
She definitely won't have to worry...

617
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:16,840
about saving up for a house like we do.

618
00:37:17,769 --> 00:37:19,119
You can now take care...

619
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:21,518
of your parents and siblings.

620
00:37:21,519 --> 00:37:22,999
You can leave all your money to them.

621
00:37:23,329 --> 00:37:24,360
She might also...

622
00:37:24,809 --> 00:37:27,360
be able to provide you with good resources.

623
00:37:28,769 --> 00:37:30,159
Your thoughts make a lot of sense.

624
00:37:31,199 --> 00:37:33,239
For someone like you and me to start from scratch,

625
00:37:33,920 --> 00:37:35,079
it's not practical.

626
00:37:35,440 --> 00:37:38,239
It'd be a waste of your great looks and impressive resume.

627
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:39,519
Han Su.

628
00:37:39,920 --> 00:37:41,360
Do you need to be so harsh?

629
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:44,400
You know I love you, right?

630
00:37:46,079 --> 00:37:47,159
Then do you know why...

631
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:50,079
I didn't struggle at all before giving you up?

632
00:37:51,159 --> 00:37:52,679
Is it because I don't love you enough?

633
00:37:53,880 --> 00:37:55,599
It's because I love you too much!

634
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:57,119
I know you too well,

635
00:37:57,199 --> 00:37:58,840
just as I know myself.

636
00:37:59,920 --> 00:38:01,640
My nature prevents me from being someone...

637
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:03,038
who goes with the flow.

638
00:38:03,039 --> 00:38:04,079
It's the same for you.

639
00:38:04,809 --> 00:38:05,880
Our lives...

640
00:38:06,199 --> 00:38:07,960
are tied down by practicality.

641
00:38:08,329 --> 00:38:10,289
There's nothing to be ashamed of in admitting it.

642
00:38:12,840 --> 00:38:14,119
So we're the same.

643
00:38:14,289 --> 00:38:15,360
The same kind of people.

644
00:38:29,920 --> 00:38:31,039
Do you love her?

645
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:33,679
I mean, your new girlfriend.

646
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:37,960
I only love you.

647
00:38:39,880 --> 00:38:40,880
Since...

648
00:38:41,769 --> 00:38:42,840
I can't be with you,

649
00:38:44,769 --> 00:38:45,769
it doesn't matter.

650
00:38:47,289 --> 00:38:48,808
Is this something you think I love to hear...

651
00:38:48,809 --> 00:38:50,079
or is it just flattery?

652
00:38:50,159 --> 00:38:51,159
It's the truth.

653
00:38:55,360 --> 00:38:57,440
Qu Yi Peng, I'm so disappointed in you.

654
00:38:58,480 --> 00:38:59,480
You're wrong.

655
00:38:59,519 --> 00:39:01,000
We're not the same.

656
00:39:01,719 --> 00:39:03,239
I do have ambitions and desires,

657
00:39:03,769 --> 00:39:05,329
but I'm not as mundane as you.

658
00:39:07,400 --> 00:39:09,199
You're too rational and smart.

659
00:39:09,719 --> 00:39:12,558
You can always assess the best benefit combinations...

660
00:39:12,559 --> 00:39:14,679
and discard unnecessary emotions.

661
00:39:15,199 --> 00:39:16,599
I believe you love me,

662
00:39:16,920 --> 00:39:18,769
but that love is only one of the parameters.

663
00:39:19,639 --> 00:39:21,239
When the expected return on that love...

664
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:23,480
isn't promising,

665
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:26,440
you gave me up.

666
00:39:28,159 --> 00:39:29,919
You did so more decisively than anyone else.

667
00:39:46,159 --> 00:39:47,159
Bye.

668
00:43:15,329 --> 00:43:17,079
(Ideal Type)

669
00:43:22,599 --> 00:43:23,599
Hi.

670
00:43:23,600 --> 00:43:24,679
Hello.

671
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:30,079
You're beautiful,

672
00:43:31,079 --> 00:43:32,639
but you're not the one I'm looking for.

673
00:43:35,400 --> 00:43:38,599
(Blind date)

674
00:43:57,199 --> 00:43:58,280
Sit down.

675
00:44:19,920 --> 00:44:21,000
You're virtuous,

676
00:44:21,840 --> 00:44:23,400
but you're not the one I'm looking for.

677
00:44:37,840 --> 00:44:39,399
You've been here all day. I'm closing the shop.

678
00:44:39,400 --> 00:44:40,480
Get lost.

679
00:44:49,440 --> 00:44:51,400
You're the true love I've been looking for.

680
00:44:53,159 --> 00:44:54,439
I've been watching you all day.

681
00:44:54,440 --> 00:44:55,598
- My true love. - Someone like you...

682
00:44:55,599 --> 00:44:56,678
doesn't deserve true love.

683
00:44:56,679 --> 00:44:57,679
Get out of my way.
